# Ticket 1 - Illegal FTP Site Investigation

## Scenario

A Security Analyst reported suspicious FTP traffic associated with copyrighted software downloads and requested identification of the FTP server hosting the content.

## Investigation

### Tools Used

* Wireshark
* FTP Protocol Analysis
* TCP Stream Inspection

### Commands

```text
ftp
Follow TCP Stream
```

### Findings

Analysis of the packet capture identified an FTP session involving unauthorized software downloads.

FTP server identified:

```text
10.10.20.2
```

## Root Cause

An unauthorized FTP server was hosting copyrighted software.

## Resolution

Documented the server IP address and created the required reporting file.

## Skills Demonstrated

* Wireshark Analysis
* FTP Investigation
* Packet Capture Analysis
* Incident Response
